OL,3,CPensioner, 92, to go on trial accused
OL,4,Cof abuse at children's home
OL,6,FA 92-year-old man is due to go on
OL,7,Ftrial next year accused of sexual
OL,8,Fabuse at a children's home more than
OL,9,F30 years ago.
OL,11,FMalcolm Phillips and his co-defendant
OL,12,FLinda Brunning, 65, were charged
OL,13,Ffollowing an investigation launched in
OL,14,F2018 into the Skircoat Lodge
OL,15,FChildren's Home, in Halifax, West
OL,16,FYorkshire.
