OL,3,CPensioner, 92, to go on trial accused
OL,4,Cof abuse at children's home
OL,6,FPhillips, of New Imperial Crescent,
OL,7,FTyseley, Birmingham, was charged with
OL,8,F32 offences, relating to seven alleged
OL,9,Fvictims, both male and female, between
OL,10,F1976 and 1994.
OL,12,FThese charges include rape, indecent
OL,13,Fassault, gross indecency and other
OL,14,Fsexual offences including two counts
OL,15,Fof aiding and abetting an unknown male
OL,16,Fto commit indecent assault.
