OL,3,CPensioner, 92, to go on trial accused
OL,4,Cof abuse at children's home
OL,6,FPhillips appeared by videolink for a
OL,7,Fhearing at Bradford Crown Court, where
OL,8,FJudge Jonathan Rose, the Recorder of
OL,9,FBradford, set a date of January 5 for
OL,10,Fthe trial, which is expected to last
OL,11,Fsix weeks.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, Brunning appeared in court
OL,14,Fin person.
OL,16,FThe defendants will be asked to
OL,17,Fofficially enter pleas to the charges
OL,18,Fat a later hearing, the court heard.
